node.text: @Nespresso asked me, George Clooney and more coffee lovers to tell what “Care is” for us 🙏 Care to me is supporting our online and offline communities, because together we are stronger 💪 I’m so proud to be part of Nespresso’s game changing movement “Made with care” This is our commitment to use our voices and all our means, including coffee, to become a catalyst for positive change and I’m also so excited to announce that from today I’m officially part of Nespresso’s family ☕ I want you guys to watch this video and share in the comments what care means to you 😘 #adv

In this video I ask newspapers and all media to take responsibility of what they write. 
I talk about victim blaming, slut shaming, revenge porn and double standards in our society.
This is my invitation to take action, to stand up and speak up, it’s time that we start supporting each other and build a better society starting from today.

node.text: This video is my beauty and digital revolution ✌️On Monday 2nd of Nov I did my first Beauty Live show, to present my capsule collection with @lancomeofficial and the show was 100% live streaming. More than 49k people connected during this live and they could comment, like and (the best part) shop live, without even leaving the page 😍 My Lancome x Chiara Ferragni Absolu Drama Matte "Working Girl" lipstick went sold out during the live and we had more than 200k interactions from all of you guys who watched the show live 💘 I want to thank Lancome, for being so forward thinking and for supporting me in this innovative idea, @anniemazzola, my incredible co-host of the show, @annadellorusso @valentinaferragni @veronicaferraro and @lisaeldridgemakeup for joining me in this memorable moment 🙏 This is just another amazing step of the future of ecommerce, marketing and beauty 💙 #adv
